data.title: 2013 Knockin' Around These Blues
data.meta_description: John Primer & Bob Corritore's first album! They decided to join forces to deliver a Chicago Blues Masterpiece! Majestic performances by two masters with an ALL-STAR BAND: BARRELHOUSE CHUCK, CHRIS JAMES, PATRICK RYNN, BOB STROGER, BILLY FLYNN, BRIAN FAHEY AND KENNY "BEEDY EYES" SMITH SONGS: 1) THE CLOCK 2) BLUE AND LONESOME 3) WHEN I GET LONELY 4) CAIRO BLUES 5) LEANIN' TREE 6) HARMONICA JOYRIDE 7) LITTLE BOY BLUE 8) JUST LIKE I TREAT YOU 9) MAN OR MOUSE 10) GOING BACK HOME
data.text:
John Primer & Bob Corritore's first album! They decided to join forces to deliver a Chicago Blues Masterpiece! Majestic performances by two masters with an ALL-STAR BAND: BARRELHOUSE CHUCK, CHRIS JAMES, PATRICK RYNN, BOB STROGER, BILLY FLYNN, BRIAN FAHEY AND KENNY "BEEDY EYES" SMITH SONGS: 1) THE CLOCK 2) BLUE AND LONESOME 3) WHEN I GET LONELY
